<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA521_02_SU_0003_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema521_su_02.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema521_02_su_0003">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="1" lang="y">사과의 무게를 나타낸 것입니다. 180과 같거나 큰 수를 나타내는 방법을 알아봅시다.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <article class="page page_1">
          <h3 lang="y">무게가 180 g과 같거나 무거운 사과의 무게를 모두 선택해 보세요.</h3>

          <div class="boolean_wrap apple_weight">
            <button class="a_item" data-answer-single="true">
              <span class="num">180 g</span>
            </button>
            
            <button class="a_item" data-answer-single="false">
              <span class="num">170 g</span>
            </button>

            <button class="a_item" data-answer-single="true">
              <span class="num">181 g</span>
            </button>

            <button class="a_item" data-answer-single="false">
              <span class="num">179 g</span>
            </button>

            <button class="a_item" data-answer-single="true">
              <span class="num">183 g</span>
            </button> 
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="page page_2"> 
          <h3 lang="y">180과 같거나 큰 수를 어떻게 나타내면 좋을지 이야기해 보세요.</h3>
          
          <div class="apple_weight">
            <div class="a_item">
              <span class="num">180 g</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="a_item">
              <span class="num">170 g</span>
            </div>

            <div class="a_item">
              <span class="num">181 g</span>
            </div>

            <div class="a_item">
              <span class="num">179 g</span>
            </div>

            <div class="a_item">
              <span class="num">183 g</span>
            </div> 
          </div>

          <div class="flex justify_center">
            <div class="input_wrap">
              <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
              <div class="example_box">
                <p lang="y">‘같거나’, ‘큰 수’의 앞 글자를 따서 180과 같큰 수라고 부르면 좋을 것 같습니다.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="page page_3">
          <div class="summarize_wrap">
            <div class="summarize promise">
              <label lang="y">약속해 볼까요</label>

              <div>
                <span lang="y">180, 181, 183과 같이 180과 같거나 큰 수를 180</span><button class="reveal_btn" data-pair="1" lang="y">이상</button><span lang="y" class="small-gap">인 수라고 합니다.</span>
              </div>

              <div>
                <span lang="y">180 이상인 수를 그림에 나타내면 다음과 같습니다.</span>
              </div>

              <div class="flex cont_set">
                <div class="left-side">
                  <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA521_02_SU/0003_bg_check_01.png" alt="자 이미지">

                  <p class="t01" lang="y">179</p>
                  <p class="t02" lang="y">180</p>
                  <p class="t03" lang="y">181</p>
                  <p class="t04" lang="y">182</p>
                  <p class="t05" lang="y">183</p>
                </div>

                <div class="right-side">
                  <p class="t06" lang="y"><span class="red-dot"></span> 은 180이 <br>포함된다는 것을 <br>의미해요.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
          <button class="btnSample">예시</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
